- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper discusses the graph representation of the network structure and the dynamics of the system, which can be seen as a type of social and information network. 
- q-bio.QM (Quantitative Methods): The paper applies quantitative methods to analyze a biological regulatory network. 
- q-bio.TO (Tissues and Organs): The paper focuses on a regulatory network involved in T helper cell differentiation, which is a topic related to tissues and organs.
